      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading configurations or uncertainty in loading is explicitly quantified.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 loading configuration only. Clinically, screw constructs experience a range of lordotic angles and offset distances not represented here. This factor is below the required level; the gap is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory context of a single standardized test."
