    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single below-level factor (Test conditions, achieved=2 vs. required=3) reflects the limitation of a single standardized F1717 loading configuration; this gap is accepted because the regulatory submission is scoped to the F1717 protocol and the quantitative output comparison satisfies all acceptance criteria with margin. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence context.",
